CREATE TABLE `artists` (
  `Id` int NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `ArtistId` int NOT NULL,
  `Score` decimal(10,2) NOT NULL,
  `Label_Boost_Score` decimal(10,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `Timestamp` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `SMR_Score_Active` decimal(10,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `SMR_Score_Historic` decimal(10,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `Post_Mentions_Score_Active` decimal(10,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `Post_Mentions_Score_Historic` decimal(10,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `Views_Score_Active` decimal(10,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `Views_Score_Historic` decimal(10,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `Social_Score_Active` decimal(10,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `Social_Score_Historic` decimal(10,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `Videos_Score_Active` decimal(10,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `Videos_Score_Historic` decimal(10,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `Spins_Score_Active` decimal(10,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `Spins_Score_Historic` decimal(10,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `Releases_Score_Active` int NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `Releases_Score_Historic` int NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `Posts_Score_Active` decimal(10,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `Posts_Score_Historic` decimal(10,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  PRIMARY KEY (`Id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=914 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1
